{"parse":{"title":"Large Raw Mightfish","pageid":113824,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||15}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_MonsterHead_02\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=13893\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=55\n|name=Large Raw Mightfish\n|level=45\n|effect=Use: Restores 1392 health over 30 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nThis item can be caught in either the Swamps of Sorrow or the Blasted Lands. You needed to have a fishing skill level of 350. Catch rate for this item at a skill level less than 350 was 6%.\n\n==Large Raw Mightfish as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Mightfish Steak}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13893}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/large_raw_mightfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]"}}}